message.body: Hey miss, are you done homeworking and around and free tomorrow night?
Hello!!! I actually have one more final, Monday morning. Then I get my life back and I expect to see you!!!
Ok whew! Awesome. My no alcohol no dairy no sugar diet ends tuesday! Perfect!
Oh I am def on that train too, save the celebratory booze post exams, so we can eat salads together and forever.
Oh wait. I read that wrong
Ill be starting to watch what I put into my body instead of wolfing pizza but no matter!
